gboard.com/p/the-death-of-the-small-point-guard?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=280925&amp;post_id=193685293&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The Death of the Small Point Guard?</a></strong> by  </p></li>\n<li><p>🏀 <strong><a href=\"https://www.burdsofafeather.com/p/death-taxes-and-joel-embiid-injuries?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=5933793&amp;post_id=193786545&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Death, Taxes, and Joel Embiid Injuries</a></strong> by  </p></li>\n<li><p>🏀 <strong><a href=\"https://blessyourchart.substack.com/p/182-ripple?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=1185822&amp;post_id=193354182&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Ripple: A look at past Final Four success and a new era of Carolina basketball.</a></strong> by  </p></li>\n<li><p>🏀<strong>▶️</strong> <strong><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Tw1UZc3f1Io\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The trade that ruined the Wizards</a> </strong>by <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@SecretBaseSBN\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Secret Base</a></p></li>\n<li><p>🏈 <strong><a href=\"https://startkyleorton.substack.com/p/dare-to-be-average-cam-ward-and-the?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=8160360&amp;post_id=192917702&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Dare to Be Average: Cam Ward and the Year Two Leap</a></strong> by  </p></li>\n<li><p>🏈 <strong><a href=\"https://www.splitzoneduo.com/p/dabo-swinney-fire-coaches?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=2043967&amp;post_id=192472347&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Dabo’s Decline and the History of CFB’s Guy After the Guy</a></strong> by  </p></li>\n<li><p><strong>🏈 <a href=\"https://thespade.substack.com/p/a-data-driven-mock-draft?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=1892935&amp;post_id=191395004&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">A Data Driven Mock Draft</a></strong> by  </p></li>\n<li><p>🏈 <strong><a href=\"https://www.golongtd.com/p/nfl-scouts-on-the-most-polarizing?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=222258&amp;post_id=193678293&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">NFL scouts on the most polarizing prospects in the 2026 NFL Draft</a></strong> by  </p></li>\n<li><p><strong>🏈 <a href=\"https://www.footballfilmroom.com/p/2026-nfl-draft-indiana-qb-fernando?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=606027&amp;post_id=193502477&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">2026 NFL Draft: Indiana QB Fernando Mendoza Breakdown</a></strong> by  </p></li>\n<li><p><strong>🏈 <a href=\"https://grindingthemocks.substack.com/p/2026-risers-and-fallers-two-weeks?utm_source=post-email-title&amp;publication_id=3891054&amp;post_id=193608394&amp;utm_campaign=email-post-title&amp;isFreemail=true&amp;r=gwh9&amp;triedRedirect=true&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">2026 Risers and Fallers: Two-Weeks Out Edition</a> </strong>by  </p></li>\n<li><p>⚾ <strong><a href=\"https://mikeshardballblueprint.substack.com/p/sandy-alcantara-miami-marlin